high_descs: Walk in the direction of the wall to the left and perpendicular to the door on your right, hang a left to the cupboard directly above the microwave oven on the other side of the room.
Open the cupboard door and pick up the green and yellow sponge, close the cupboard.
Turn around and walk to the stool to the left of the table in the center of the room.
Place the sponge in the bowl on the table directly in front of the stool.
Pick up the bowl with the sponge in it.
Walk toward the direction of the door, hang a right and walk toward the window.
Place the bowl with the sponge in it on the second shelf from the bottom to the left of the window.
anns.task_desc: Pick up a sponge, put it in a bowl, put the bowl on a shelf

high_descs: Turn and go to the cupboard by the sink.
Pick up a sponge in the cupboard.
Turn and go to the counter.
Put the sponge in a bowl on the counter.
Pick up the bowl on the counter.
Turn and go to the shelves in the corner.
Put the bowl on the shelves in the corner.
anns.task_desc: Move a bowl with a sponge to the shelves in the corner.

high_descs: Walk around the table and to the microwave to the right, then look up.
Open the cabinet door, remove the sponge inside and close the cabinet.
Look down, turn around and walk straight to the stool.
Place the sponge inside the bowl sitting on the counter to the right of the stool.
Grab the bowl with the sponge inside.
With the bowl with the sponge inside, look up, and walk to the shelf to your right.
Place the bowl with the sponge inside on the shelf.
anns.task_desc: Place a bowl with a sponge inside on the shelf.
